    "description": "Storage Guys是一款休闲多人合作游戏，你和你的朋友将扮演仓库团队的角色。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/c0a5d6afafb6b803f61b81a248944d11.webp?t=1764959486\" width=450 height=50 /></span><br>你的工作是接收物品，在仓库中整理和管理它们，然后通过正确的出货口将其发出。每次成功的发货都会让你赚钱！每个物品都有一个出货区域标签，因此你需要将它们分类并送到对应的出货口。但要注意有效期，你必须在物品过期前发货！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/314185bc9983d781b02b2ee3230efa7b.poster.avif?t=1764959486\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/314185bc9983d781b02b2ee3230efa7b.webm?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/314185bc9983d781b02b2ee3230efa7b.mp4?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/f6e7e457c4869ec82f7baae5590d76e5.webp?t=1764959486\" width=450 height=50 /></span><br>管理各种入库的物品，每种物品都有其独特的储存需求。有些需要特别照顾，而有些则更容易处理。使用称为储存间的专用房间来存放需要特殊储存条件的物品，如冷冻室、危险物品储存间和UV储存间。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/a08eae610a0ea9c0f52a25d8b9816991.poster.avif?t=1764959486\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/a08eae610a0ea9c0f52a25d8b9816991.webm?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/a08eae610a0ea9c0f52a25d8b9816991.mp4?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/a89afc82c490100b808601010d16217f.webp?t=1764959486\" width=450 height=50 /></span><br>通过仓库终端进入商店，购买货架、储存间、设备和装饰品来升级你的仓库。随着你赚到更多的钱，你可以扩展你的仓库空间，扩大业务并储存更多物品。自定义你的仓库以增强功能性并提升外观。使用不同的货架，添加储存间和设备，并装饰你的仓库，使其独特且吸引人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/d5535264ebe62a0500cc59f53f7d4a41.poster.avif?t=1764959486\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/d5535264ebe62a0500cc59f53f7d4a41.webm?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/d5535264ebe62a0500cc59f53f7d4a41.mp4?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
